{"tid":1818983,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"浦澤直樹懸疑怪獸新作 《朝陽劇場","createTime":"2020-01-10T11:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T05:46:12.000Z","uid":84696,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"8f29759936ab5275d86fd70a47adc90b5e577357","tid":1818983,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:20:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p3MBAKF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp3MBAKF.jpg&h=e7c7aa62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GnOTCX1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGnOTCX1.jpg&h=fa2fb50e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n故事由2020年東京奥運地方出現大怪獸展開序幕<br />\n<br />\n1959年，女孩朝陽在名古屋遭受強烈颱風期間，被一位前飛行員的小偷叔叔捉走。其後二人因災難成為亦師亦友，她長大後更成為飛行員，亦開始發現當年天災的神秘生物是真實存在......"},{"pid":"378b57e13b08566155b441a2f1b506ce5bc3861a","tid":1818983,"uid":29297,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:32:38.000Z","msg":"又準備爛尾？"},{"pid":"fa4b1e7ae5e178b0a49fb6a665654750347b86e5","tid":1818983,"uid":84696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"378b57e13b08566155b441a2f1b506ce5bc3861a","tid":1818983,"uid":29297,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:32:38.000Z","msg":"又準備爛尾？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T13:30:52.000Z","msg":"我諗都唔算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d16fd2f4d07ea708763626186fe47e3c2816e143","tid":1818983,"uid":157304,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"378b57e13b08566155b441a2f1b506ce5bc3861a","tid":1818983,"uid":29297,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T11:32:38.000Z","msg":"又準備爛尾？"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T14:09:35.000Z","msg":"Billy bat邊有爛尾？神作"},{"pid":"326a79583eae1de7053c5620ba8aac655765054a","tid":1818983,"uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T14:11:42.000Z","msg":"冇睇好多集,原來講怪獸架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal